messages.messageBody:
Helen,
That is funny! We were there off of Spinnaker road. I haven't been to
Alaska in nine years but my brother in law tells me they paved Hollywood
and Vine! Can you believe it? When we lived there though we still had
moose on our front porch and ( me hopping up and down ) on the path to
the out house! I miss it.
Deb L

> No kidding? Our only daughter was born one cold windy morning in a
> small cabin her father and I built about a mile off Knik Road, on
> Vine, back when it was still a dead end road... Small world. <g>
>
> Helen
